  <description type="morphology">Annuals, 10–50 cm. Stems scabrous to glabrate, not stipitate-glandular. Leaf blades linear-lanceolate, 30–60 × 2–6(–10) mm. Involucres ± turbinate. Phyllaries 5–10 × 1–2.5 mm, ± equal, usually scabrellous and stipitate-glandular. Ray florets 0. Disc florets 5–30; corollas actinomorphic, 7–10 mm, throats ± funnelform, shorter than lobes. Cypselae 5–8 mm; pappus scales of inner cypselae (1.5–)3–8 mm. 2n = 20.</description>
